TITLE: Implementing onRequest Hook
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement the onRequest hook which is called before making a request. This hook receives and must return the request context, allowing for request modification before execution.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bekacru/better-fetch/blob/main/doc/content/docs/hooks.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { createFetch } from "@better-fetch/fetch";

const $fetch = createFetch({
    baseURL: "http://localhost:3000",
    onRequest(context) {
        // do something with the context
        return context;
    },
})
```

