TITLE: Defining Query Schema for Fetch in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to define a query schema for a fetch request. The query schema describes the expected structure of the query parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bekacru/better-fetch/blob/main/doc/content/docs/fetch-schema.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
