TITLE: Linear Retry Strategy in Better Fetch (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates how to implement a linear retry strategy in Better Fetch, specifying the number of attempts and delay between each attempt.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bekacru/better-fetch/blob/main/doc/content/docs/timeout-and-retry.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_3

